			 <dd><blockquote>
        <p><font color="#FF0000">(updated April 15, 1999)</font></p>
        <p><br>
        Originally Compiled by <a href="mailto:peter.lake@planetquake.com">Kurt Kowitz</a>(used
        with permission). <br>
        Formatted by <a href="mailto:dmm2editor@aol.com">Richard Neff</a> <br>
        <br>
        This is an attempt to answer the most frequently asked questions on the Half-Life map
        editing list and the discussion board, as well as any email we get.&nbsp; This FAQ was
        originally compiled by Kurt Kowitz and replicated to Rust with permission. &nbsp; If you
        have a question to add to it then email us the question and the answer. Thanks.<br>
        <br>
        <font color="#000000">Press Ctrl+F to search for a specific word or phrase (Assuming your
        browser supports the find command.)</font></p>
        <table width="75%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" valign="TOP" bgcolor="navy"
        bordercolor="navy" bordercolorlight="navy" bordercolordark="navy">
