          <tr>
            <td><b><font color="White">WorldCraft Setup</font></b></td>
          </tr>
        </table>
        <blockquote>
          <b><p><a href="http://halflife.gamedesign.net/resources/worldcraft2_setup.shtml">Worldcraft
          2.0 for Newbies</a></b> (http://halflife.gamedesign.net/resources/worldcraft2_setup.shtml)
          <em>The purpose of Worldcraft 2.0 for Newbies is to provide the information necessary to
          install, configure, and start using Worldcraft 2.0 beta. No prior editing or editor
          knowledge will be assumed.</em>&nbsp; <strong>Note: This replaces the Inital Configuration
          tutorial. </strong>~<a href="http://halflife.gamedesign.net/">HalfLife Resource Center</a>
          </p>
        </blockquote>
        <blockquote>
          <p><b><a href="http://www.planethalflife.com/wavelength/levels/resources/setupwc.html">How
          to Setup WorldCraft 2.0</a></b>
          (http://www.planethalflife.com/wavelength/levels/resources/setupwc.html)<br>
          <em>This FAQ is designed to help you get WorldCraft setup</em>. ~<a
          href="http://www.planethalflife.com/wavelength">Wavelength</a> </p>
        </blockquote>
        <blockquote>
          <p><b><a href="http://halflife.gamegurus.net/map/setup/">WorldCraft Setup &amp; Bug List</a></b>
